The Iron Fist is the new Alliance base, and yeah, they're near it.


::Havoc/Iron Fist::

Havoc tries to spin, but the blast takes out the right half of his 
torso, the bot yelling in pain underwater. He looks ahead, the Iron 
Fist so close....

A panel slides aside, ready for the pod and Havoc to drift in. Above 
the water, the defences of the Iron Fist turn toward Angel Prime, 
multiple missile launchers firing a signature-seeking missile each at 
him, along with a volley of blasts from laser cannons. It was only 
one bot, so the ship didn't throw too much at him. The shields went 
up, ready for an attack.

Havoc swims on, but about to pass out, his vision blurring.
